
This directory - user_files - houses ALL of the files that the Supermon2
user can configure. There are NO configurable files in the supermon2
directory. Do NOT change permissions of files. See the various example
files for configuration ideas. 

     CONFIGURABLE FILES IN THIS DIRECTORY
     ------------------------------------

authini.inc      - ini to user mapping. Named Xauthini.inc to deactivate
authusers.inc    - button to user maaping. Named Xauthusers.inc to deactivate
allmon.ini       - The default Sueprmon2 initialization file
nolog.ini        - The NOT logged ini file if ini to user mapping is activated
global.inc	 - User configuration settings
favorites.ini    - Favorites button configuration
controlpanel.ini - Control Panel button configuration
background.jpg	 - This is a symbolic link to a header background image of your choice.
		   By default linked to cyborg_hamradio.png

      FILES A USER MAY ADD -  Replace <username> with real login username.
      --------------------------------------------------------------------

<username>-allmon.ini 		- Additional ini files for other users. Replace <username>
                        	  with real login username.
<username>-favorites.ini	- Favorites ini files mapped to users 
<username>-controlpanel.ini	- Control Panel ini files mapped to users

An_image_file.jpg     - Replacement for header background symbolicly linked to background.jpg

 EXAMPLE AND BACKUP FILES
